subtitle: Hello everyone, welcome back to Astral Doorway, I'd like to thank all the new subscribers
so many kind comments, people asking questions, and just really interested in this topic of
astral projection and in what i have to share so i really appreciate that, if you haven't already
click the bell button so you know when i upload a new video as there will be many videos on the way
so on this episode i'll be talking about another experience i had this week which relates to the
experience i shared which involved me stumbling upon a temple in the astral and attending
a class led by a priestess and there were around 100 unconscious participants there with me,
there's a link for that on the screen now if you would like to listen to that first, now
in this experience i tried a little experiment with these unconscious people
in the astral i tried to wake them up i tried to make them conscious that they were out of body,
now a lot of people come out of body every night unconsciously; i made a video explaining a bit
about this in my episode called lucid dreaming vs astral projection and i will be making a
similar video to that one where i will be going even deeper and clarifying about the fact that
we can have shared dreams and non-shared astral projections too, but for now let me describe this
interesting experience which towards the end was quite funny uh but really this whole experience is
me being a bit bad really uh i shouldn't have done what i did in a way so anyway, so before this
main astral projection i became lucid in a dream now usually when i become lucid in a dream i
immediately intend to brush off the entire nonsensical narrative of the dream and go straight
into actual projection, however, just before i was about to do that i noticed there were two women in
my dream shouting and arguing with each other so i just observed with a silent mind, i contemplated
the scene and realized that i was in a sort of broken part of me, like there was a split inside
me, inside my subconscious, that was arguing with each other i felt the negative energy of it,
the unconsciousness of it, so i just breathed and meditated and focused on my heart area and sort of
consumed the dream you could say with the intention of healing it, of unifying it, as i did
this everything became black i entered a sort of void of peace, and after this, i felt my awareness
very slowly come back to my body the transition was so slow that i was able to bring myself
back out of body to find myself standing in my room next to where i was sleeping,
so while i'm out of body i walk around my house and enter the living room and i see my girlfriend
sitting on a chair next to our dining table and she's just browsing on her phone ,quote-on-quote
"phone", since we're in the astral any sort of objects can usually be conjured up like this
whether consciously or unconsciously now in this moment i know that her physical body is actually
fast asleep in bed next to mine so clearly she's out of body unconsciously, so since i've been kind
of at this stage of my spiritual investigations uh you know investigating people out of the body
unconsciously recently um i got this completely random idea to try and see how aware she actually
was and see if i can make her conscious of herself so, i go over to her with a big smile on my face
and say "hey!" now she says "hello" back casually, i can tell she's unconscious i say to her in a
slow and intimate way really trying to connect with her, "do you know that we're in the astral
right now?" she says "yes" in a kind of dreary way i know that that wasn't really a conscious answer
now she knows a bit about the astral since i talk about it to her but she's not exactly at the point
of understanding it or practicing it, per se, which is normal like most people of course, anyway
so i say to her "hey lookm do this with me" and i show her how to do the
'hold nose reality check,' uh you may be familiar with this already from lucid dreaming
reality check methods if not you can simply google it, it also works in the astral because
the astral is also non-physical it simply involves using your fingers to close your nostrils shut
and if you can breathe through your nostrils while they're shut then you're in the non-physical but
if you can't breathe through them then you're in the physical so she does the reality check and as
she's doing it something starts to happen, i feel a shift with her and i ask her "is it working?"
she says "yes" nodding as she keeps doing it, and she keeps doing it more intensely
her eyes start to become wider and she starts to look confused, now what happens next was strange,
i started to see another body of her, an exact double of her, which was a bit transparent,
it started to slowly enter the room and merge with her, it wasn't merging with her yet it was just
in the room and it was going towards her it was slowly about to enter her body, as if you imagine
an out of body experience happening but reverse the process, so my theory on this is that her
fragmented consciousness or awareness was actually more centered within another dream world, you know
we are multi-dimensional beings after all i don't deny the fact that in these
non-physical dimensions we can be in multiple places at the same time,
just in the same way that in the physical we can think multiple thoughts at the same time, or that
we can be in a physical location but be completely somewhere else in our heads too,
uh but i'll get into all that on one of the next videos anyway, so yeah as i saw this other body of
hers about to merge with the one that i was next to, she started to feel a lot of fear,
she looked very scared i immediately saw this as dangerous you know she's my partner i don't
want to cause any fear or whole possible damage to her psyche, and not that it would
do any damage i think but i just felt in that moment that the right thing to do was to stop,
you know just as i feel in the physical i don't believe it's ever right to try and force people to
awaken i believe when people are ready they will awaken naturally and gradually, nature has a way
of doing this gracefully you know i've not made this channel to preach i've just made it for
the few people in the world who are genuinely interested in this topic of astral projection,
you know who am i to try and do such things to people? anyway and so while i
saw her panicking and this other body about to merge with her astral body, so to speak,
i just rubbed her back and comforted her i i said "hey it's okay, you can stop, everything's fine"
and i quickly just saw her and everything else go back to normal and with that i just intended
to leave immediately, i flew through the wall of my house in a fast speed with the intention to
just come out on the other side absolutely anywhere in the world i didn't care where,
and as i went through the wall everything went black i felt this intense energy as i always do
when teleporting somewhere further away and i was unconscious for a few seconds and boom,
i find myself somewhere in america i don't know why i ended up there perhaps it's because i speak
to a lot of americans online who knows, i suspect i was somewhere around new york / manhattan area
because it had that real busy working vibe, i was stood on a pavement, and i saw yellow taxis,
burger joints, these huge skyscrapers and just lots of people on the streets,
i've never been to new york, but i had a pretty good hunch that that's where i was, now
i guess i just didn't really learn from what just happened with my girlfriend because
i still had this intention to see what would happen if i woke an unconscious person up in the
astral, my curiosity just hadn't been satisfied you could say, uh you could call me a sort of
evil scientist next because i basically went on a hunt to find some test subjects
so i walked down the street for a bit and i found a small grocery store on the ground floor
of a tall building, there were a lot of people inside so i jumped up and went through the ceiling
to get to the next floor the next floor was empty so i jumped through to the second floor there were
only a couple of people there, so i kept jumping floors until i found one that i could work with
and eventually i found a floor with an office, it was a sort of open plan office with about eight
people inside everyone was dressed smart and all busy doing work, uh this is quite common in the
astral a common thing that people do unconsciously out of the body, you know people just do things
they would do in the physical people in the astral just go to work sit around their house, do chores,
you know mundane things that they usually do in the physica,l anyway i interrupt them all and
say loudly to all these office workers, "hey do you know that you're all actually asleep?
this isn't the physical plane it's the astral plane!", now most of them just look at me
blankly but a few are slightly interested or confused so again i show them all the 'hold nose
reality check' and tell them all to do it, most of them actually start doing it i asked them
"is it working?" now of course it is working but most of them are, they seem so unconscious
that they're just like "yeah" nodding their head not really realizing the true impact of
what's going on, now there were a couple of women in the room, one of them had a similar reaction
to my girlfriend and looked very confused and almost scared but another woman actually started
to become excited she said "yes oh my god, wow, it's working!" i was amazed and i just studied her
for a bit, she was this middle-aged lady with this sort of wild expression on her face now,
um i said to her, "hey look don't you want to take a break from work? you can do anything you want,
go anywhere in the world that you like..." she said very excitedly ,"yes i want to go to africa!"
i said "okay great let's go! all you have to do is think about it", she had this
smile and determination on her face for a bit but i could see that she was
struggling to go to africa and she said, "i can't do it, it's not working" i said "no no it's fine
it will work, i'll do it with you" so i stand next to her and put my arm around her shoulders
and i told her to chant this with me, "i want to go to africa!" and we chanted in
unison "i want to go to africa! i want to go to africa!" the energy was building up
and as we're saying this everything turned black for a moment but i could still feel her with me
and then, as if by magic, we end up in this dry desert wilderness with various african-looking
bushes and trees and we can see the sea with a beach in the distance beyond some vegetation
she's still next to me and i say to her "you see? beautiful, you didn't need to be at work!"
now i have to admit personally i didn't think it was the most scenic place there were too
many twigs and branches on the ground and the ground was very dry and cracked there were
also vultures around us and a lion not too far from us, nevertheless she's ecstatic and starts
cheering and running and dancing around, and i just stand there laughing watching her celebrate
now she spotted the beach in the distance and she started to run towards it but
in order to get to it she had to get through some of these bushes and trees so
what happened next was um she was trying to get through the bushes and the trees
but i saw the lion start to chase after her, i just froze at this point i didn't know what to do
the lion jumped into the bush and i hear her scream now, i'm just basically like oh
[ __ ] right, (haha) i was just watching the bush and i couldn't make out what was happening but i
assumed a lie and tried to maul her to death right or something, uh remember we're in the astral so
nothing that bad can happen, all animals have astral bodies too by the way i'll make
a video for that in the future, anyway she then comes out of the bush and looks at me
and she uh she basically came out as half lion half human, it was a hilarious sight,
she had her human face with a mane, paws on her hands and feet, and a tail and she
was like almost double in height, and on top of that her dead-blank expression of confusion and
shock was just an absolutely hilarious sight to see uh i'll have to draw a picture sometime
um it makes me evil for laughing right now but at the time i wasn't laughing i was
just as confused and as shocked as her i had no idea what just happened, but thinking about it
now and the image of her blank expression uh is just gold, astral gold, um of course i felt bad
too uh you know what had i just made this lady go through? she was attacked by a lion and basically
half shape-shifted into one? i don't know how she managed that but it was my fault that she had this
and confusion uh so as we're looking at each other blankly, uh suddenly
without my own will everything turned black for a few seconds and i was pulled into a room,
and you guessed it i was unexpectedly in another astral classroom, and the first
thing i hear immediately was the teacher saying "okay we're going to take a break, just relax"
and he just left the room and put students inside by ourselves, now i'm not sure
what that meant whether someone was watching me and realized i was messing with people
but anyway i just went with the flow at this point uh was i part of this class before? i don't know,
i at that time i had felt bad for what i had just done to this lady, the lion lady,
and i didn't feel the most proud about sharing it so i just went with the flow really i don't know
what happened, this was completely unexpected, now this wasn't an astral classroom like the
temple experience i shared, i could see that the, around 10 of the students who were in the room,
were also conscious like me i didn't get time to ask questions or get introductions because
everyone seemed pretty focused on just doing various activities, i had a sense that everyone
else had just been astral traveling too, and that they were perhaps a bit tired like me
i sat opposite this girl who looked in her early 20s and i sensed that she was actually an astral
projector too, there's no real indications for why i felt that it was just really an intuition
and also i thought that because she looked tired as if she was struggling to maintain her awareness
but that she was doing a good enough job to keep herself grounded here, on the other hand i sensed
the guy who was sat on the right of me was very conscious but i don't think he had a physical body
i saw that because he was very energetic and very awake compared to everyone else,
talking to people about various things and spiritual subjects...
a couple of people showed me how to play a board game that was similar to chess
except there were a few different rules, it was interesting when you picked up a piece
the board would light up tiles to show you where you could go, i must have played that for a good
10 minutes, after that i got bored a bit and i noticed we had these sort of holographic
floating computers in the room that i wanted to use, the talkative guy next to me noticed
that and jokingly said "you're not just going to find channels to subscribe to on there are you?"
i just laughed and said "no i don't really know what i can look for on here", now i have been
out of body for a while at this point and i must have looked a bit like the girl who
sat opposite me as i started to sense this experience was perhaps coming to an end,
however this guy seemed so alert and awake i think he was definitely a permanent inhabitant here,
anyway he used the computer next to me and said "hey actually, look, this is interesting..."
now what was cool was he got up these images from the computer but they weren't just
on the screen they actually came out of the screen and projected into 3d
glowing holograms in the air, he got up all these beautiful images of elder-warrior looking people,
in front of stone buildings they wore these beige cotton tribal sort of clothes,
and also an image of the milky way galaxy which was a bright white and blue with a sort of
bright yellow sun in the middle, like the one you can see on the screen, and he also got up another
galaxy next to it which looked similar but it had sort of a more green hue color, it was a beautiful
sight to see, and as i was looking he said "look, these people are the people of Lemuria and
actually these people didn't live connected to our galaxy, they were more connected to THIS galaxy",
pointing to the more green looking galaxy, he showed me the name of it but i don't remember
it well because it was just some sort of code, now i don't know anything about Lemuria
i know a bit about atlantis i think they're connected maybe but i've only vaguely heard
about Lemuria once or twice many years ago i've not looked into the topic at all so it came as
a surprise to me i believe Lemuria was meant to have existed thousands of years ago towards
asia or something? i had to do a bit of googling but i still couldn't find much information on it
and i really wanted to see if there was any art or descriptions of what they wore or how they
lived to see if it was similar to the images that i saw, so if any of you have any links or
resources to show me anything like that that would be great just leave a comment below, especially if
there's any information about what they apparently wore or what types of buildings they lived in,
but yeah i was pretty impressed with that astral computer, was it a computerized expression of the
akashic records? who knows i didn't get time to ask because as i was looking up at these images
floating in the classroom i woke up and quickly wrote down the entire experience all the way up to
when i was in that dream with the woman arguing at the start... so yeah a big lesson from this
experience for me is you just can't go around trying to wake people up, it's of little use
really, on reflection i still think the lion lady was not fully aware of what was really happening
and i doubt she retained any memory of it she could have i hope she did uh who knows,
one question that i can tell people will ask and what many people have asked before is,
"is it possible to pull people directly out of their physical body?" now you probably
could pull someone out but i think two things are most likely to happen, 1: the person just
comes out unconsciously or 2: they're conscious but they don't remember it anyway, you know even
for someone like me who trains my non-physical memory to remember these experiences all the time,
you know i can remember up to seven different dreams every morning sometimes or more,
but still sometimes i can go all day until the evening and then suddenly remember that i had an
astral projection or lucid dream actually that happened right before i started this recording,
it's about five o'clock in the afternoon right now, i woke up at around 10 a.m this morning
and right before i did this recording i realized oh i remembered that i became lucid in a dream
um i can remember doing the reality check, but i can't recall any memory of it, so the likeliness
of people remembering you pulling them out of their body is going to be very
small people need to align their intent and desire and practice to remember these
experiences themselves, that's why i always say you know always recall all your dreams,
and even all the insignificant details of them ,whether it's a dream or astral projection,
it really helps with this non-physical memory part of our brain... so thanks for listening
everyone please like and subscribe if you enjoyed the video and i will see you on the next episode
